<h2>ðŸ“Š Dataset Information</h2>
<p><b>Dataset Name:</b> Vehicle Dataset 2024<br>
<b>Source:</b> Kaggle<br>
<b>File Used:</b> car_data_clean.csv</p>

<table>
<tr><th>Feature</th><th>Description</th></tr>
<tr><td>Range (km)</td><td>Distance per full charge</td></tr>
<tr><td>Top Speed (km/h)</td><td>Maximum specified speed</td></tr>
<tr><td>Efficiency (Wh/km)</td><td>Energy consumption per km</td></tr>
<tr><td>Acceleration (0â€“100 km/h)</td><td>Time taken to reach 100 km/h</td></tr>
<tr><td>Seats</td><td>Seating capacity</td></tr>
<tr><td>Price (USD)</td><td>Target variable</td></tr>
</table>

